com.github.MudPitBot.botCommand

Class CommandReceiver

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.MudPitBot.botCommand.CommandReceiver

  • public class CommandReceiver
extends java.lang.Object
    A receiver class for command pattern. A receiver is an object that performs a set of cohesive actions. It's the component that performs the actual action when the command's execute() method is called. https://www.baeldung.com/java-command-pattern
